{
  "stem": "25348.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "She already had a friend who could have been her father, and he was a Volksdeutsche called Huber.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "When she introduced him to me and she said his name was Huber, I thought to myself, next thing she's going to tell me, he's German.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He was a Volksdeutsche.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But I have to tell you this as a prelude to what it all amounts to, to my survival.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Huber was in the administration of Todt building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Todt, I don't know whether you are familiar-- the Todt Organization, named by former [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think armament minister for-- in Germany.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He arranged-- it was a widespread organization which, in occupied territories, had-- was responsible for extending railway lines and building fortifications.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And Huber tutored me, how I go into the office.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I don't look at him, and I don't know him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And he will give me a job in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He knew who I was because Christina told him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Anyhow, I secured this job in the kitchen peeling potatoes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I was peeling potatoes till my cuticles sort of were bleeding.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I was hoping they were bombs, and I was throwing them into water all the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "To make it short, my job-- also why I'm telling you, it might sound trivial-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] my job also included, in the afternoon, cleaning the room of four German supervisors.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "You see, the Todt Organization brought with them workers, skilled workers from another place, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "It was a hole.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "So they brought some skilled workers from Warthegau, electricians and people like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But the Germans, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [NON ENGLISH] as they were called, the supervisors, they kept sort of-- they separated themselves from them.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
